  "text": "In earlier published work [CITATION_1] , organizational characteristics were derived that pertain to SME information security. The research described in this paper follows up on those previous efforts by further evaluating the organizational characteristics and their measurement levels, and how they pertain to the ISFAM maturity matrix through a survey.",
